<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_94a83bdf-f1ff-40fa-a05d-45c68d4cd1bd" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>J6D11</sptc><title id="_c204c1e6-bf14-4b25-b8d8-621635c17074">Refrigerant chillers</title><archive-num/><subclause id="_0123f1d0-134c-42bd-a9c7-8da6986f366e" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_4adf3cd7-e4e4-4da6-a769-49e28972abeb">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Refrigerant chillers must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_3911e01d-41ea-42bf-b7b7-42f0315f91d0">individually, comply with (2); or</li><li id="_10a33dff-f521-4078-8e55-9bf31489b3d0">collectively, comply with (3).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_19629c3d-3ba7-48a6-83e4-147c7d9e34f6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_9fd45b0a-8da9-4efb-bd99-cff9f86ecdbb">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>When assessed in accordance with AHRI 551/591, a chiller must—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f92599ef-739b-4917-a0c3-b678073dda7f">where air-cooled—<ol><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_423d0a4b-0003-4b3d-95c8-34cbb5cf2e22" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 1 or 3, achieve a full load operation energy efficiency ratio of not less than 3.1; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_8ded65aa-ef72-4ed5-8855-fa32d912aced" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 2, 4, 5, 6 or 7 achieve a full load operation energy efficiency ratio and an integrated part load value such that the sum of the two is not less than—<ol><li>8.1, where the rated cooling capacity of the chiller is not greater than 550 kW; and</li><li>8.5, where the rated cooling capacity of the chiller is greater than 550 kW; and</li></ol></li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_ef594a59-27a4-451b-8846-5ad00b72b0d0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zone</xref> 8, achieve an integrated part load value of not less than—<ol><li>5.1, where the rated cooling capacity of the chiller is not greater than 550 kW; or</li><li>5.4, where the rated cooling capacity of the chiller is greater than 550 kW; and</li></ol></li></ol></li><li id="_69e4d0a4-fd9a-4126-87e3-d1b11884bf3b">where water-cooled—<ol><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_311355ef-24e5-4a51-b047-5bd2076d5657" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 1 or 2, achieve full load operation energy efficiency ratio of not less than the value specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/112_0.23.0.xml#_75fc0156-9005-4536-91c5-1f164252f4c0" id="_02044158-5271-4334-99e0-3363fb0014f6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J6D11a</xref>; and</li><li>in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1458_0.16.0.xml#_0d25cef7-0651-40ea-a0e6-3d3db1191e24" id="_56d59efd-0b8f-4e23-9b21-5ed6b8d6637a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate zones</xref> 3 to 8, achieve a full load operation energy efficiency ratio and an integrated part load value such that the sum of the two is not less than the sum of the full load and integrated part load values specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/112_0.23.0.xml#_75fc0156-9005-4536-91c5-1f164252f4c0" id="_33c152ed-4217-437e-8c80-642257edd738" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J6D11a</xref>, as applicable.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_751c9e05-d607-4dc2-87b3-e91f311f8cee" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_096d0aab-d411-4830-9992-fbe208bcd889">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>A connected group of one or more refrigerant chillers, used as part of an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1181_1.0.0.xml#_386d327a-f182-4f1a-bf21-5cfdef50cc8d" id="_53f7704a-2520-4d41-9534-5fe0ac7f5bbb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">air-conditioning</xref> system, must achieve a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/9431_0.3.0.xml#_fc66c3e7-45c3-4184-96c8-b34170b296d8" id="_e09ecdfd-73b2-41a6-8d6b-be5eefbdd8db" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">climate specific part load value</xref>, determined in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/9854_0.5.0.xml#_7e5eef7a-5a6d-409a-9451-98645ca47b43" id="_32c5a675-0df3-4d68-ac63-eab7d0757f3f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="specification">Specification 47</xref>, greater than—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e29f8979-d46e-427f-96c5-d0c4c6a3e66c">the applicable value specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/113_0.16.0.xml#_e89325a0-4686-4e99-b2d4-d206499eec16" id="_cc6fa3ca-085f-4e72-9ba7-28f4a376f767" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J6D11b</xref>, where all chillers in the group are water-cooled; or</li><li id="_3b991318-ef59-4929-b623-d26d558a6956">the applicable value specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10144_0.4.0.xml#_fd3dc8c8-9367-4a7c-af54-b645322dda6c" id="_5117a3c9-a1f4-466c-ac44-f698e173ee61" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J6D11c</xref>, where all chillers in the group are air-cooled; or</li><li id="_486940fe-c2ee-4e55-8d8c-b68be6e8dbcd">the average of the applicable values specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/113_0.16.0.xml#_e89325a0-4686-4e99-b2d4-d206499eec16" id="_9c660a12-6397-4927-9359-6db573eb193a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J6D11b</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10144_0.4.0.xml#_fd3dc8c8-9367-4a7c-af54-b645322dda6c" id="_e214284b-d198-430e-8bd5-64f3de516f2d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table J6D11c</xref> weighted according to the total full-load capacity of the chillers, where the group has both water-cooled and air-cooled chillers.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_3adcf41f-1284-4a12-855d-e78c79cf164c" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_40ed589c-6190-450c-b798-713264f7aeec">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>The requirements of (1), (2) and (3) do not apply to—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f83ab7dd-0984-42ca-8316-92eac6119a5e">4-pipe chillers; or</li><li id="_ddd7bee8-1c88-448d-90b4-a8d8ca462344">air-source heat pump water heaters.</li></ol></subclause><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/112_0.23.0.xml" graph="None" id="_75fc0156-9005-4536-91c5-1f164252f4c0"><num/><title id="_dcf04d66-6cdf-47de-9be4-fe58b2fe312e"/></table-reference><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/113_0.16.0.xml" graph="None" id="_e89325a0-4686-4e99-b2d4-d206499eec16"><num/><title id="_795760fe-0a74-4523-9283-2be03e3f8fc7"/></table-reference><table-reference author="Jerome Samuel" conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/10144_0.4.0.xml" dateTime="2024-09-02T11:57:11" graph="None" id="_fd3dc8c8-9367-4a7c-af54-b645322dda6c" type="insert"><num/><title id="_3119678c-28d6-4eb4-8174-2663e15153dc"/></table-reference></clause>